    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are not-assessed at level 1, consistent with MRL 2 requirements per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. No unacceptable weakeners identified. Decision: Accepted for regulatory submission.",
